title: 求救 无法注册矿物，注册矿物已被占用 如何修改
author: weidan02123
txt_content:
Time: 7/8/19 12:29 PM
Description: There was a severe problem during mod loading that has caused the game to fail

net.minecraftforge.fml.common.LoaderExceptionModCrash: Caught exception from Pewter (pewter)
Caused by: slimeknights.tconstruct.library.TinkerAPIException: [TCon API] Could not register Material "osmium": It was already registered by Metallurgy 4: Reforged
        at slimeknights.tconstruct.library.TinkerRegistry.error(TinkerRegistry.java:951)
        at slimeknights.tconstruct.library.TinkerRegistry.addMaterial(TinkerRegistry.java:129)

replies.author: mine新时代xs
replies.txt_content:
魔法匠魂模组尝试向匠魂2注册“锇”这种材料，但你添加的冶金4重制版与匠魂有联动，已经添加了这种材料
唯一的办法是作出取舍，删除魔法匠魂或者冶金4重制版
或者你可以看看它们两个的配置文件，或许可以禁用和匠魂的联动或者禁用“锇”这种材料，由于我对这两个模组无比陌生，没有它们的配置文件，所以你得自行查看

replies.author: a135252320
replies.txt_content:
建议更新一下pewter和Metallurgy 4: Reforged这两个模组，作者好像修复了这个冲突
FYI：https://github.com/ejektaflex/Pewter/issues/82
